 W_1 = \left \{ \begin{bmatrix}a & a\\0 & b\end{bmatrix}: a,b \in R  \right\} \ and \ W_2 = \left \{ \begin{bmatrix}c & d\\c & 0\end{bmatrix}: c,d \in R  \right\}
 W_1 + W_2
W_1 \bigcap W_2
W_1 + W_2
\left \{ \begin{bmatrix}a+c & a+d\\c & b\end{bmatrix}: a,b,c,d \in R  \right\}
U+V=\{u+v|u\in U, v\in V\}
